$ Overpass API: settings

{ bbox

  Use the `{{bbox}}` extension:
code {
[bbox:{{bbox}}];

nw[amenity=restaurant];

out center;
code }

code {
[bbox:
    49.8727,  // min lattitude: south border
    -6.4458,  // min longitude: west border
    49.8730,  // max lattitude: north border
    -6.4452   // max longitude: east border
];

//
// Select all nodes, ways and relations in
// the area selected by the bounding box
// setting:
//
nwr;

out;
code }

  The following query gets the bounding box of the «current view»:
code {
[bbox:{{bbox}}];
out bb;
code }

}

sa:

  The → development/OpenStreetMap/API/Overpass/settings/out[`out`] setting.

  is unrelated to the `→ development/OpenStreetMap/API/Overpass/statements/out` statement.
